added six anomaly and average, fixed agdd refactor bugs
fixed base 32 50 bug, bloom peaks bug, and changed six species avg to use nan for unreported values
changed six anomaly to use day 365 30yr average and cookie cutter requested date
intitial check in of qc gdd checker
just date change
pycharm update

changed is to ==
historic ncep yearly handling
saving nightly six image function, commented out

added gdd checker to run at the end of gridded models nightly update script

taking out passwords and paths
removing log file
